One of the things you all have forgotten,<P>on a bad pull of that nature you have other options as long as the tanks are keeping the mobs off ... <P>start to take a look at the usefullness of your AE line of spells... when you get a bunch of monsters and they are all bunched up use the ability to damage them all with the same mana.. likely you will need to work this in as an add since no one wants 4 mobs agrroing on them but this will shorten the lifespan of the mobs that your not concentrated on and shorten the battle making it not as close as it could be.<P>Just a thought   <IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/eq/smile.gif">
