Benevolents one thing you should know is that quite honstly you are in for a long hard road of pain and suffering. this is not to discourage you but it is the truth, i never played a more challenging newbie toon as when I started my wizard, now I am not huge (only lvl 24 now) but at lvl 20 the whole world gets a little brighter. people start to say "sure we could use a wizard" and your spells are more worth casting. Dont be discouraged, cause all Ive heard thus far is that the higher your lvl the better it gets   <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0"><P>--------------------<P>Caldavien X'Teriak<BR>Wizard Of Eci<BR>Follower of Innorruk<P>"For the glory of Innorruk We fight and for the glory of Innorruk we die, but for the sheer power alone! We choose to hate."<BR>                 Caldavien X'Teriak
